[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent, longitudinal-store initialization with cross-system data hydration, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading with care-pathway-state computation, conversation handling with care-pathway-grounded responses and pending-action awareness, output safety screening with scope and citation verification, warm-handoff routing to human care coordinators when applicable, care-team reporting with consent enforcement, and audit logging with care-coordination-specific retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (cross-system data integration as architectural primitive, care-pathway-as-code with clinical-leadership ownership, pending-action ledger with closed-loop tracking, cross-provider conflict flagging with routing, and equity-focused per-cohort monitoring as launch-gate discipline).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution app, payer portal,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    care-management workflow, or post-discharge handoff]  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to care-coordination    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      assistant interaction with cross-system integration │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-source data-sharing consent matrix            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (per source system, per data category, per          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      destination, per purpose)                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-on-behalf-of-patient consent where        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      applicable                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Crisis-resource information surfaced                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    confirmation; initialization of longitudinal store]   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE + CROSS-SYSTEM HYDRATION ───┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-assistant longitudinal store]                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions on the problem list               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current care team (per provider with role and       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      contact)                                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active care plans (per condition)                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active referrals (per referral with status)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Upcoming appointments                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent labs and imaging                              │
