[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Cross-system hydration]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR (Patient, Condition, MedicationStatement,       │
