[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Payer eligibility                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy refill history                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Lab results system                                  │
