[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-management system                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management platform                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Health Information Exchange (where available)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants resource directory              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed per       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Sensitive-disclosure surface: separately governed   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
