[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported)                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Assistant-initiated entry]                            │
